{"tid":784721,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"（急）有無連登獸醫或有經驗主人","createTime":"2018-08-18T15:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T10:25:58.000Z","uid":23871,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8bfb0878d8a290037bfc1206d1b567ca704e3864","tid":784721,"uid":23871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:22:38.000Z","msg":"狗狗最後呢3日都精神唔好 又胃口麻麻 今日睇左獸醫 <br />\n獸醫建議我地安排狗狗住院幫佢吊鹽水同做檢查<br />\n<br />\n暫時抽左血知道佢啲腎指數高 同埋有啲貧血 <br />\n仲有驗尿都結果都話佢啲尿液較稀 唔正常。<br />\n但宜家獸醫都比唔到個diagnosis我地 <br />\n<br />\n狗仔本身有甲狀腺低食左藥一個月左右 今日驗埋血見佢甲狀腺宜家變左過高 想知道會唔會係啲甲狀腺藥令搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：狗狗已經入左院 只係想聽多個意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7e2cd65fe48dfde37572e0f352ccc7c1d77bc0","tid":784721,"uid":79326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T04:57:48.000Z","msg":"留tg俾我"},{"pid":"853f2e81bb47929f125378db182910ea086f2a42","tid":784721,"uid":23871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d7e2cd65fe48dfde37572e0f352ccc7c1d77bc0","tid":784721,"uid":79326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T04:57:48.000Z","msg":"留tg俾我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:25:58.000Z","msg":"唔該巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/k712j\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fk712j&d=ilbAUjjR90mprNH%2BEJ%2FAJsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=9fb36629\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/k712j</a>"}]}